 ability to create customized formulas, calculations and reports, import national cost indexes, compare subcontractor and vendor quotes, track jobs by divisions and sub-divisions and store digital images to enhance your estimates.","<strong>Ease of Use</strong><br/>Construction and commercial work can be complex, but estimating software doesn t have to be. The best applications have a gentle learning curve and are accessible to anyone with a working understanding of the construction business.","<strong>Integration</strong><br/>If you don&#39;t currently use commercial estimating software, you re likely using some sort of spreadsheet or financial software to track your costs and other data. The best commercial estimating software integrates with other applications to import and export this data.","<strong>Help &amp; Support</strong><br/>The level of customer support a package offers is an important consideration when using such powerful and complex software. The best packages offer several outlets for training and demonstrations.","While no software can take the place of innovative ideas, hard work and competitive bids, an outstanding commercial estimating software solution goes a long way toward taking the guesswork and tedium out of estimating and completing construction projects of all kinds."]},"id":"3363e5bd-1c36-46c3-9c97-117d395986c2","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Related Product Reviews"},"id":"7d234679-951e-41a9-93bc-97293898a168","type":"heading"},{"data":{"items":["<a href=\"http://www.softwareadvice.com/construction/cost-estimating-software-comparison/price-quotes/?utm_source=TopTenReviews&utm_medium=affiliate\">Estimation</a>","<a href=\"http://www.softwareadvice.com/construction/cost-estimating-software-comparison/price-quotes/?utm_source=TopTenReviews&utm_medium=affiliate\">ProEst</a>","<a href=\"http://www.softwareadvice.com/construction/cost-estimating-software-comparison/price-quotes/?utm_source=TopTenReviews&utm_medium=affiliate\">Sage</a>","<a h